{"id":71663,"title":"Physical and mental health among cancer survivors: considerations for long-term care and quality of life.","abstract":"The physical and mental health of cancer patients needs to be addressed not only during active treatment but also throughout the continuum of survivorship care. This commentary provides an overview of issues pertinent to cancer survivors, with an emphasis on mental health issues and recommendations for annual clinical screening and monitoring using recently published guidelines from the American Society of Clinical Oncology. ","date":"2014-07-22","categories":"Neoplasms","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25046097","annotations":[{"name":"Mental health","weight":0.818686,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mental_health"},{"name":"Health","weight":0.730357,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Health"},{"name":"Quality of life","weight":0.718103,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Quality_of_life"},{"name":"Therapy","weight":0.705583,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapy"},{"name":"Cancer","weight":0.603461,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cancer"},{"name":"Oncology","weight":0.551693,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oncology"},{"name":"Screening (medicine)","weight":0.462149,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Screening_(medicine)"},{"name":"Mind","weight":0.403648,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mind"},{"name":"United States","weight":0.366983,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/United_States"},{"name":"Clinical psychology","weight":0.286427,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Clinical_psychology"},{"name":"Cancer survivor","weight":0.2695,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cancer_survivor"},{"name":"American Society of Clinical Oncology","weight":0.215579,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/American_Society_of_Clinical_Onco